>> Read the chisq column, not just p. If chisq falls FASTER than the SNP
>> count, the surviving SNPs are not merely fewer -- they are a
>> COMPOSITIONALLY DIFFERENT subset. That is a stronger claim than power
>> loss, and the numbers above decide it. Do not assert it without them.

